name: Pocket C.
text: The pizza was good, and so was the boneless chicken bites. The establishment has a dim old school feel to it. The ordering was a bit of a hassle; some items weren't available, some weren't even out yet, and there wasn't as much variety when you look for food outside the pizza. But!!! The pizza was delicious.

text: It was our first time there. We took my wife's niece/nephew. It was good. The pizza was good. I liked the crust a lot. Kids had fun as they were able to play some games.

name: Gloria Mejia
text: Good pizza friendly staff! We like coming here for dinner or lunch , the salad bar is usually fully stocked and fresh. It's a little pricey but worth it. Get the wings extra well done, taste much better.

text:
Good food like always but even better was the service we received today. We had the lunch buffet and they went out of their way to bring us fresh pizza to our table as they came out of the oven. Very friendly people.
We will definitely return
